1019},"getBlockNumber",[961,1127,1100],{"class":970},[961,1129,1103],{"class":974},[961,1131,1132],{"class":963,"line":213},[961,1133,1134],{"class":970},"])\n",[1136,1137,1139],"h3",{"id":1138},"components","Components",[1141,1142,1143,1159],"table",{},[1144,1145,1146],"thead",{},[1147,1148,1149,1153,1156],"tr",{},[1150,1151,1152],"th",{},"Component",[1150,1154,1155],{},"Lives in",[1150,1157,1158],{},"What it does",[1160,1161,1162,1182,1193],"tbody",{},[1147,1163,1164,1176,1179],{},[1165,1166,1167,1168,1171,1172,1175],"td",{},"Injected Provider (",[947,1169,1170],{},"window.ethereum",", ",[947,1173,1174],{},"window.nimiq",")",[1165,1177,1178],{},"WebView (injected by Nimiq Pay)",[1165,1180,1181],{},"Exposes wallet APIs and sends requests to the host",[1147,1183,1184,1187,1190],{},[1165,1185,1186],{},"Host-side API",[1165,1188,1189],{},"Nimiq Pay (native)",[1165,1191,1192],{},"Receives requests, validates them, shows approval dialogs, executes actions",[1147,1194,1195,1198,1201],{},[1165,1196,1197],{},"Mini App SDK (optional)",[1165,1199,1200],{},"WebView (your app or injected)",[1165,1202,1203,1204,1207],{},"Typed Nimiq-native APIs + ",[947,1205,1206],{},"Result\u003CT, E>"," patterns; uses its own message format",[930,1209,1210,1211,1213,1214,981],{},"Your mini app uses standard Web3 APIs via ",[947,1212,1170],{}," and Nimiq-specific APIs via ",[947,1215,1174],{},[1136,1217,1219],{"id":1218},"request-lifecycle","Request lifecycle",[1221,1222,1223,1227,1230,1233,1236],"ol",{},[1224,1225,1226],"li",{},"Your mini app calls a provider method (for example, request accounts or sign a message)",[1224,1228,1229],{},"The injected provider forwards a message to the Nimiq Pay app",[1224,1231,1232],{},"The Nimiq Pay app validates the request and shows a native confirmation dialog (when required)",[1224,1234,1235],{},"If approved, Nimiq Pay executes the wallet operation (keys never leave the wallet)",[1224,1237,1238],{},"The result is returned to your mini app through the provider",[925,1240,1242],{"id":1241},"supported-networks","Supported Networks",[930,1244,1245],{},"The framework supports two blockchain ecosystems:",[930,1247,1248],{},[1249,1250,1251],"strong",{},"Nimiq",[1253,1254,1255,1258],"ul",{},[1224,1256,1257],{},"Native support for NIM payments, message signing, and consensus checks",[1224,1259,1260],{},"Direct integration with Nimiq Pay's core wallet features",[930,1262,1263,1266],{},[1249,1264,1265],{},"Ethereum + Layer 2 networks"," (EVM-compatible)",[1253,1268,1269,1272,1275,1278,1281,1284,1287],{},[1224,1270,1271],{},"Ethereum Mainnet",[1224,1273,1274],{},"Polygon",[1224,1276,1277],{},"Arbitrum One",[1224,1279,1280],{},"Optimism",[1224,1282,1283],{},"Base",[1224,1285,1286],{},"BNB Smart Chain (formerly Binance Smart Chain)",[1224,1288,1289],{},"Sepolia (testnet for developers)",[930,1291,1292],{},"Any EVM-compatible chain supported by our RPC provider can be added; the list above reflects what we currently expose in Nimiq Pay. Additional EVM networks can be added over time via configuration updates.",[925,1294,1296],{"id":1295},"security-and-permissions","Security and Permissions",[930,1298,1299],{},"Every sensitive action requires explicit user approval through native dialogs that mini apps cannot bypass. Your app runs in a secure sandbox with no direct access to private keys. The Nimiq Pay app mediates all wallet operations.",[930,1301,1302],{},"Here's how security works:",[1253,1304,1305,1311,1317,1328],{},[1224,1306,1307,1310],{},[1249,1308,1309],{},"User consent is always required",": Viewing accounts, signing messages, and sending NIM payments trigger native confirmation dialogs",[1224,1312,1313,1316],{},[1249,1314,1315],{},"Sandboxed execution",": Mini apps run in an isolated WebView with no access to the wallet's internal state or private keys",[1224,1318,1319,1322,1323,1327],{},[1249,1320,1321],{},"Host app controls everything",": Your app can only ",[1324,1325,1326],"em",{},"request"," actions. The Nimiq Pay app decides whether to fulfill them, always with user approval",[1224,1329,1330,1333],{},[1249,1331,1332],{},"Wallet requests are mediated",": Nimiq Pay handles wallet-related provider requests, while other RPC calls use the configured endpoint or your mini app's own RPC",[1335,1336,1337],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .spNyl, html code.shiki .spNyl{--shiki-light:#9C3EDA;--shiki-default:#C792EA;--shiki-dark:#C792EA}html pre.shiki code .sTEyZ, html code.shiki .sTEyZ{--shiki-light:#90A4AE;--shiki-default:#EEFFFF;--shiki-dark:#BABED8}html pre.shiki code .sMK4o, html code.shiki .sMK4o{--shiki-light:#39ADB5;--shiki-default:#89DDFF;--shiki-dark:#89DDFF}html pre.shiki code .s7zQu, html code.shiki .s7zQu{--shiki-light:#39ADB5;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-default:#89DDFF;--shiki-default-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#89DDFF;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic}html pre.shiki code .s2Zo4, html code.shiki .s2Zo4{--shiki-light:#6182B8;--shiki-default:#82AAFF;--shiki-dark:#82AAFF}html pre.shiki code .swJcz, html code.shiki .swJcz{--shiki-light:#E53935;--shiki-default:#F07178;--shiki-dark:#F07178}html pre.shiki code .sfazB, html code.shiki .sfazB{--shiki-light:#91B859;--shiki-default:#C3E88D;--shiki-dark:#C3E88D}html pre.shiki code .sBMFI, html code.shiki .sBMFI{--shiki-light:#E2931D;--shiki-default:#FFCB6B;--shiki-dark:#FFCB6B}html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-de